OL,3,CScottish Government has 'failed'
OL,4,CDisclosure Scotland waiting times,
OL,5,CLabour says
OL,7,FThe Scottish Government has "failed"
OL,8,Fto provide Disclosure Scotland with
OL,9,Fthe resources it needs to complete
OL,10,FProtection of Vulnerable Groups (PVG)
OL,11,Fchecks on time, Scottish Labour has
OL,12,Fwarned.
OL,14,FThe party said on Sunday that "urgent
OL,15,Faction" is needed to cut waiting times
OL,16,Ffor PVG checks, after revealing data
OL,17,Fthat found 11,875 applications took 42
OL,18,Fdays or more to complete between April
OL,19,F1 and December 31 last year.
OL,26,@oD@]OUoD@dO]vD@_OUwD@GO]
