OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784539118
OL,3,CScottish Government has 'failed'
OL,4,CDisclosure Scotland waiting times,
OL,5,CLabour says
OL,7,FSome 20,441 applications took between
OL,8,F28-41 days, 45,355 waited between 15
OL,9,Fand 27 days, and 257,061 took between
OL,10,F0-14 days to complete.
OL,12,FThe official target timeframe is 14
OL,13,Fdays or fewer.
OL,15,FThe longest wait was 301 days, and the
OL,16,Flongest suspension time was 146 days.
OL,18,FAll those who work with children or
OL,19,Fvulnerable people are required to have
OL,20,Fa PVG check conducted before they
OL,21,Fstart employment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
