CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784539118
OL,3,CScottish Government has 'failed'
OL,4,CDisclosure Scotland waiting times,
OL,5,CLabour says
OL,7,FScottish Labour education spokeswoman
OL,8,FKatherine Sangster said: "These checks
OL,9,Fare vital in keeping children and
OL,10,Fprotected adults safe from harm.
OL,12,F"However, these figures show that
OL,13,Fthousands of checks are now taking
OL,14,Fmuch longer than the 14-day target for
OL,15,Fcompletion.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
