PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784539118
OL,3,CScottish Government has 'failed'
OL,4,CDisclosure Scotland waiting times,
OL,5,CLabour says
OL,7,F"This not only makes it more difficult
OL,8,Ffor those working in roles such as
OL,9,Fteachers, nursery practitioners, or in
OL,10,Four health service, to begin work, it
OL,11,Falso presents challenges for those
OL,12,Forganisations already struggling with
OL,13,Fstaffing shortages.
OL,15,F"A well-functioning disclosure system
OL,16,Fis a matter of public safety, but
OL,17,Funfortunately, the SNP government has
OL,18,Ffailed to provide Disclosure Scotland
OL,19,Fwith the resources it needs to carry
OL,20,Fout robust and speedy checks.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
