OL,3,CScottish Government has 'failed'
OL,4,CDisclosure Scotland waiting times,
OL,5,CLabour says
OL,7,F"Ministers must urgently act to ensure
OL,8,Fthe organisation has the support it
OL,9,Fneeds to cut the backlog and bring
OL,10,Fdown the wait times for these
OL,11,Fimportant checks to be completed."
